  Destructor emerged from his cr chamber a new man. His powers fully 
restored. He yawned and hoped famine had finished the final testing. He 
contacted him on the comm..."Is it prepared?"...."Yes sir..come when ready."
  Hw walked towards the door where kit kat sleeped. He opened the door with 
his own captian override in case it was locked. He watched her sleep for a 
moment. Not wanting to wake her. He glided his hand across her cheek..."Wake 
up...we are ready."
